Chapter 0
Introduction
These lecture notes are based on a week-long seminar class taught by Dr. Francesco Maggi at UT Austin at the summer RTG
Analysis and PDEs seminar. These cover introductory topics related to calculus of variations, such as rst and second variation
formulae, gradient ows, and related arguments.
